cent!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Solid</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/keshande/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9940da9f2f4229b2b184107f80d7f1fe?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9940da9f2f4229b2b184107f80d7f1fe?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/keshande/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">keshande</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 17, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We\'ve really enjoyed the functions and features of Formidable Forms. It has become a part of our trusted tools to use in all of our websites.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">GOOD PLUGIN</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tboy52/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aca58a07c39e3986fb970fb74b6e53a0?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aca58a07c39e3986fb970fb74b6e53a0?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tboy52/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tboy52</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 16, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The formidable form is an excellent plugin, easy to use, and straightforward. It collects data easily and I get notification on my email address.\n\nOne of the best here</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">bait and milk-out</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bundelmedia/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b4a4e2284e5412642bd2ca991012de29?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b4a4e2284e5412642bd2ca991012de29?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/bundelmedia/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">bundelmedia</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 15, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I was looking for a formbuilder with calculations for my client. Seeing the Formidable Forms\' excellent presentation of features (and example Mortgage calculators) I got super excited that I\'ve found what I needed. \nOh how short lived that excitement was.\nCalculator fields are not available in the free version: ok, understandable - plenty other form builders do that too. But... $199 ?! Seriously?\nFluent forms: $59\nGravity Forms: $59 (and with addiotional $59 addon, VERY advanced calculations)\nNinja Forms: 0\nJetForms: 0</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Download to find out its NOT free</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/the-newb/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a60e754478f6c1b449a099c5c5305fa6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a60e754478f6c1b449a099c5c5305fa6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/the-newb/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">The Newb</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 10, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">another bait and switch $$$</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">It&#039;s like Jotform, but with a soul. (and more features)</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/waypointwell/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9b7e32d15e262aebcdb3bc62a6d363a5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9b7e32d15e262aebcdb3bc62a6d363a5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/waypointwell/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">waypointwell</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 9, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">For anyone who is looking to develop a web application formidable is a great option. I\'m still just scratching the surface but I feel vindicated from my underwhelming Jotform/wpForms/Gravity experience. So many saas solutions exist in the form creation category and they focus on just that aspect. Prices vary wildly for really similar capabilities and yet once you\'ve built your \'tool\' you feel handcuffed. Especially if your are dealing with sensitive information (HIPAA compliance). \n\nThere is a feeling of ownership and also very responsive support. They also have a strong community of users willing to share advice on slack and a growing list of developers who are starting to see the potential and offer turn-key solutions.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great- does a ton of stuff</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/buck7287/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a6fd3df1ab24b04a0c305c033b7d9ab9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a6fd3df1ab24b04a0c305c033b7d9ab9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/buck7287/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">buck7287</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 4, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using formidable forms for about a month now and I really like all the capabilities. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Best out there</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jajja/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/786f4de6b2ef08dea37f3dabddb085be?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/786f4de6b2ef08dea37f3dabddb085be?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jajja/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jajja</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 28, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve tried many form builders. Formidable beats them all.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The Best Plugin I&#039;ve Ever Utilized!!!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/abidefiler/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f4d760bcb457043aa2b227aebfd501b8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f4d760bcb457043aa2b227aebfd501b8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/abidefiler/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">abidefiler</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 25, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I love Formidable Forms So Much!\n\nWe\'re getting ready to launch with only two months of Dev time, and part time, 1 to 2 hours per day.\n\nThank you Formidable Forms!\n\nNow, if you can help me find a GREAT Marketing and Launch Connection...</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/umizen40/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/46629be3448e5586c5f6dc7c8313270e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/46629be3448e5586c5f6dc7c8313270e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/umizen40/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">umizen40</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 24, 2022</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I use it since 8 years without any issue. Thanks !</div>\n</div>\n\";}}','no'),(5188,'_transient_timeout_frm_form_fields_1excl