','field_625d1894ea1da'),(3159,409,'property_type','Ground-up house build'),(3160,409,'_property_type','field_625d18a5ea1db'),(3161,409,'text_content','<h1>The Scenario</h1>\r\nThe Borrower had obtained planning permission on a property to erect 2 additional houses on the land. They then attempted to sell the property with the planning gains via auction. The Property did not sell, and the existing lender’s term was soon to expire without the possibility of loan extension.\r\n\r\nInflow re-bridged the property with a view to the ‘flip’ as the exit strategy. The borrower then proposed that they would like to carry out the development. Whilst the borrower had significant experience in the property market as an investor, he had not undertaken ground up development. Inflow was able to work with the borrower and seamlessly switch the loan to a development facility enabling the borrower to carry out the project with cost of works being funded.\r\n\r\nDue to the pandemic the development time frame expanded and the build costs increased. Inflow was able to extend the time frame with no penalties applied, understanding the developer’s requirements and the development opportunity.'),(3162,409,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(3163,409,'add_section_image','457'),(3164,409,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(3165,409,'add_section_image_s','456'),(3166,409,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(3167,409,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">A ground up development loan for a First time Developer</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Flexibility provided throughout the loan term</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Product switch with minimal fuss (residential bridge to development facility)</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Inflow’s experienced team liaised with the developer\'s team of professionals to cover risk parameters and structure a suitable development loan.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3168,409,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(3169,409,'choose_similar_case_studies','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"412\";i:1;s:3:\"408\";i:2;s:3:\"410\";}'),(3170,409,'_choose_similar_case_studies','field_625d41b95a5b8'),(3171,303,'add_hero_background_color',''),(3172,303,'_add_hero_background_color','field_625d2f985a5b5'),(3173,303,'hero_background_image',''),(3174,303,'_hero_background_image','field_625d2fb65a5b6'),(3175,303,'text_content','<h1>The Scenario</h1>\r\nA borrower had sourced a deal that they wanted to complete before the stamp duty hike (June 2021). The broker contacted Inflow to provide a loan to facilitate the purchase, requiring completion within 5 days.\r\n\r\nThe Inflow Team was able to offer terms, organise valuers and instruct solicitors, all on the day of enquiry to enable completion to take place on time. Inflow’s priority service helped the borrower save £18k in Stamp Duty Land Tax.'),(3176,303,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(3177,303,'add_section_image','457'),(3178,303,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(3179,303,'add_section_image_s','456'),(3180,303,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(3181,303,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Inflow works with industry-leading professionals to enable speed of service</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Solicitors and Valuers instructed the same day, providing priority service</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Inflow were able to make fast decisions by taking a commercial approach.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3182,303,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(3183,303,'choose_similar_case_studies','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"306\";i:1;s:3:\"301\";i:2;s:3:\"409\";}'),(3184,303,'_choose_similar_case_studies','field_625d41b95a5b8'),(3185,301,'add_hero_background_color',''),(3186,301,'_add_hero_background_color','field_625d2f985a5b5'),(3187,301,'hero_background_image',''),(3188,301,'_hero_background_image','field_625d2fb65a5b6'),(3189,301,'text_content','<h1>The Scenario</h1>\r\nA seasoned developer with a large portfolio was looking to refinance an outstanding bridging loan and also seeking a  refurbishment facility. The borrowers had achieved planning to redevelop the flat into a large family unit including adding a rear extension and landscaping.\r\n\r\nThe existing lender was not able to provide the facility for cost of works nor provide an extension to the borrowers. Inflow intimately understood the project by liaising with borrowers, their brokers, the project architects and our surveyors. The solution provided competitive refurbishment terms with a 100% cost of works facility.'),(3190,301,'_text_content','field_625d1ef55af51'),(3191,301,'add_section_image','457'),(3192,301,'_add_section_image','field_625d1f285af52'),(3193,301,'add_section_image_s','456'),(3194,301,'_add_section_image_s','field_625d1f3a5af53'),(3195,301,'text_content_s','<h1>Key Highlights</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Inflow were able to provide a large loan with built in flexibility and offer a suitable refurbishment product</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">100% Cost of Works</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">A key understanding of the development, location and the intended finish of the project to reflect the GDV potential.</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3196,301,'_text_content_s','field_625d1f415af54'),(3197,301,'choose_similar_case_studies','a:3:{i:0;s:3:\"306\";i:1;s:3:\"303\";i:2;s:3:\"409\";}'),(3198,301,'_choose_similar_case_studies','field_625d41b95a5b8'),(3199,466,'flexible','a:5:{i:0;s:18:\"hero_section_large\";i:1;s:21:\"most_popular_products\";i:2;s:13:\"steps_section\";i:3;s:16:\"features_section\";i:4;s:25:\"most_popular_case_studies\";}'),(3200,466,'_flexible','field_624f096c944c5'),(3201,466,'flexible_0_main_title','Property finance for property people.'),(3202,466,'_flexible_0_main_title','field_624f0c38454d4'),(3203,466,'flexible_0_section_short_description','Fast, flexible, bespoke property finance solutions. '),(3204,466,'_flexible_0_section_short_description','field_624f0c54454d5'),(3205,466,'flexible_0_s