efinance or create liquidity from a freehold ground rent portfolio; we can provide Terms to suit your requirements.\r\n<h3>Probate and Tax Funding</h3>\r\nInflow can structure Terms which suit the circumstances of your tax affairs.'),(5224,299,'_first_column_content','field_627398bcedc8f'),(5225,299,'second_column_content','<h3>Planning Uplift</h3>\r\nWe are property people. If you have a perspective on planning gain for a property, talk to us.\r\n<h3>Mezzanine Finance</h3>\r\nWhere there is a requirement for additional debt capital to pursue growth opportunities, our specialist Team can understand and structure a loan solution.\r\n<h3>Large Loans (£5M+)</h3>\r\nAs a principal lender with a commercial approach, we can consider larger loans and provide lending decisions within 24 hours.\r\n<h3>Rescue &amp; Recovery Deals</h3>\r\nStructuring loans and making a deal work is in our nature. Our Team is able to offer ultrafast turnaround on lending decisions and loan completion.\r\n<h3>Special Situation Finance</h3>\r\nFor special situations, please <a href=\"#\">contact a member</a> of the Team to discuss your enquiry.'),(5226,299,'_second_column_content','field_62739b61edc90'),(5227,299,'section_background_color_kf',''),(5228,299,'_section_background_color_kf','field_6255336e24110'),(5229,299,'section_background_image_kf',''),(5230,299,'_section_background_image_kf','field_6255337124111'),(5231,299,'short_section_description_kf',''),(5232,299,'_short_section_description_kf','field_625533492410f'),(5233,299,'section_content_image_kf',''),(5234,299,'_section_content_image_kf','field_625533ad24112'),(5235,299,'section_list_items_kf',''),(5236,299,'_section_list_items_kf','field_625533cb24113'),(5237,299,'add_text_content',''),(5238,299,'_add_text_content','field_62553f042e31e'),(5239,299,'add_image',''),(5240,299,'_add_image','field_62553f212e31f'),(5241,299,'add_image_s',''),(5242,299,'_add_image_s','field_62553fc42e321'),(5243,299,'add_text_content_s',''),(5244,299,'_add