e\r\nproperty-centric</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We focus on the property to unlock its potential. This is why we assess every investment opportunity carefully to reach the decision that will suit your property needs.</p>'),(7001,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_0_add_icon_items_row_0_add_description','field_626ba79fedb76'),(7002,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_0_add_icon_items_row','2'),(7003,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_0_add_icon_items_row','field_626ba774edb73'),(7004,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections','3'),(7005,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections','field_626ba74aedb72'),(7006,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_0_add_icon_items_row_1_add_icon','519'),(7007,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_0_add_icon_items_row_1_add_icon','field_626ba78cedb74'),(7008,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_0_add_icon_items_row_1_add_description','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We believe in\r\nproperty people</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We support the SME property developer and investor market; a key segment for supplying much needed UK housing stock, which is poorly and inefficiently served by traditional funding.</p>'),(7009,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_0_add_icon_items_row_1_add_description','field_626ba79fedb76'),(7010,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_0_add_icon','522'),(7011,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_0_add_icon','field_626ba78cedb74'),(7012,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_0_add_description','<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">We keep it simple</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">One of our missions is to simplify property finance. You will speak directly to experts and decision makers, with a common-sense approach. We won’t waste your valuable time.</p>'),(7013,616,'_flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_0_add_description','field_626ba79fedb76'),(7014,616,'flexible_1_icon_items_sections_1_add_icon_items_row_1_add_icon',