ifying property finance.'),(7779,3,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Privacy Policy | Inflow'),(7780,3,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Read more about our privacy policy and how we collect and use the personal information we collect on the Inflow website.'),(7781,166,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Auction Finance | Inflow'),(7782,166,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Get your finances in order within tight auction time-frames. Prepare for an auction and secure the property you like.'),(7783,164,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Residential Bridging Loans | Inflow'),(7784,164,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','1st and 2nd charge residential bridging loans are designed for a variety of residential projects. Find out more about our criteria and terms.'),(7785,162,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Semi-Commercial and Commercial Bridging | Inflow'),(7786,162,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Discover all about semi-commercial and commercial bridging created to help you gain a competitive edge in today\'s complex market.'),(7787,158,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Refurbishment Finance | Inflow'),(7788,158,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Whether you are looking for light, medium or heavy refurbishment of your property project, refurbishment finance is the perfect solution.'),(7789,133,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Development Finance | Inflow'),(7790,133,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','A wide range of flexible development finance solutions. Find out more how Inflow can help you by getting in touch with our team.'),(7791,299,'_yoast_wpseo_title','Bespoke Finance | Inflow'),(7792,299,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','Do you need a bespoke finance solution crafted to suit your unique property needs? Share your project details with our team and get an offer.'),(7793,12,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','property finance'),(7794,12,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','43'),(7795,164,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','residental bridging loans'),(7796,164,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','38'),(7797,162,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','commercial bridging'),(7798,162,'_yoast_wpseo_linkdex','44'),(7799,158,'_yoast_wpseo_focuskw','refurbishment financ